  "texts": [
    "Implications for researchThere was a clear lack of research from low-and middle-income settings as well as vulnerable populations in all settings.",
    "Most of the included studies explored the perceptions of community dwelling older adults.",
    "More research on the experiences of older adults living in residential care or other settings could help to broaden our understanding.",
    "Very few of the studies explored perceptions of specific interventions.",
    "Most looked at treatment across interventions and participants did not differentiate between interventions in the same way a health care provider would."
  ],
